# to alearn about API's

https://restful-api.dev/

# To install API related s/w
- Install -> pip install requests

# To run APi file.
- python -\file name. (API file name needs to start always with 'api' keyword followed by anything)

# payload
payload - data that we want to send to the API. In GET request we are not sending any data to the API, 
hence it is empty.

# GET Method
- While using Get method- payload and header is empty.

# POST Method
When we use POST method we need to give payload and header values
payload is the json format (required for python coding) of request body

